  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Legal Counsel",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This high-impact, business-facing role requires a legal professional with proven expertise in financial services and digital assets to lead the full lifecycle management of corporate legal documentation and affairs, partnering closely with the General Counsel.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Draft, review, and negotiate core business contracts including Liquidity Provider agreements, client agreements, Introducing Broker agreements, payment agreements, and outsourcing agreements to support business operations and growth.</li><li>Manage the full lifecycle of contracts, ensuring timely execution, amendments, renewals, termination, and compliance with post-termination obligations.</li><li>Develop, maintain, and update standard contract templates and clauses to streamline recurring business activities and reduce legal risks.</li><li>Collaborate with business units to deliver practical, commercially focused legal advice that enables operational efficiency and supports strategic growth initiatives.</li><li>Act as the primary escalation point for resolving legal issues arising from business activities, ensuring timely and effective risk mitigation.</li><li>Provide expert legal counsel on general corporate and commercial matters including corporate governance, group structure, and daily business operations to ensure compliance and sound decision-making.</li><li>Deliver legal support on IT, data protection, and privacy matters to safeguard company interests and maintain regulatory compliance.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>LLB or equivalent degree, admitted to practice in a common-law jurisdiction such as Singapore, UK, US, or Hong Kong.</li><li>Minimum 5 years post-qualification experience combining top-tier law firm training and in-house roles within trading firms, fintech, or digital asset platforms.</li><li>Builder mentality with demonstrated ability to independently establish processes and work autonomously in a fast-paced, high-growth environment.</li><li>Proficiency in English (written and spoken) to effectively review legal documentation, negotiate contracts, and coordinate with internal and external stakeholders.</li></ul>",
